{"type":"message","id":"55acf749","parentId":"96e09995","timestamp":"2026-03-19T09:46:48.363Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see the context monitor cron job is running every 5 minutes. Looking at the script, it seems to just monitor and log the context usage but doesn't actually trigger an automatic switch. Let me re-read the skill - it mentions that the automatic switch should happen but the script itself doesn't seem to do that.\n\nLooking at the context-monitor.ps1 script I read earlier:\n- It only MONITORS and LOGS the context usage\n- It doesn't actually trigger an agentTurn to create a new session\n\nSo the current setup is just monitoring, not auto-switching. The skill says the auto-switch should happen at 60%, but it seems like the implementation is incomplete.\n\nSince this is a cron job running in an isolated session with delivery mode \"none\", it's not supposed to deliver any message to the user. The script just monitors and logs.\n\nLooking at the log, the context is at 62% which exceeds the 60% threshold. The script logs a warning but doesn't take any action to:\n1. Save memory\n2. Create a new session\n3. Notify the user\n\nThis seems like the context-manager skill is partially implemented - the monitoring works but the auto-switch mechanism isn't fully set up.\n\nGiven the current situation:\n- Context is at 62% (exceeds 60% threshold)\n- The script just logs warnings but doesn't auto-switch\n- There doesn't seem to be a complete auto-switch mechanism in place\n\nAccording to the SKILL.md, the context-manager should:\n- ✅ **自动触发**：上下文达到60%自动切换\n\nBut this doesn't seem to be happening. The current implementation just monitors and logs.\n\nLet me respond to the user about the current status and ask if they want me to implement the auto-switch functionality, or if they want to manually start a new session.","thinkingSignature":"c699e850a86fcbafb549015e1078c660be5b8251b1868e2235df61672eeb0152"},{"type":"text","text":"**Context Monitor 结果**\n\n当前主会话 `agent:main:main` 上下文使用情况：\n- **Token 使用**: 123k / 200k (62%)\n- **状态**: ⚠️ 超过 60% 阈值\n\n日志显示上下文已连续多小时保持在 60% 以上，但自动切换功能似乎尚未完全配置。当前 Context Monitor 脚本只负责监控和记录，尚未实现自动保存记忆并创建新会话的功能。\n\n**当前监控状态**:\n- 每 5 分钟检查一次 ✅\n- 超过 60% 阈值时记录警告 ✅\n- 自动切换功能 ⚠️ 未配置\n\n如需启用自动无缝切换，需要配置完整的记忆保存和 agentTurn 触发机制。是否需要我帮你配置完整的自动切换功能？\n\n或者，如果你想现在手动重置上下文，可以告诉我，我会帮你创建新会话。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":50363,"output":542,"cacheRead":37011,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87916,"cost":{"input":0.0151089,"output":0.0006504,"cacheRead":0.0011103299999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01686963}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773913585425}}
